org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.imagejdatatypes.datatypes.greyscale

Class ImagePlusGreyscale32FData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.imagejdatatypes.datatypes.ImagePlusData
      • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.imagejdatatypes.datatypes.greyscale.ImagePlusGreyscaleData
        • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.imagejdatatypes.datatypes.greyscale.ImagePlusGreyscale32FData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeData, GreyscaleImageData

    public class ImagePlusGreyscale32FData
extends ImagePlusGreyscaleData
    32 bit float greyscale image without dimension. These image data types exist to address general processing solely based on bit-depth (e.g. process all 2D image planes). Conversion works through ImplicitImageTypeConverter
